<br>
Unsure whether or not to tip his hand, but with curiousity getting the best of him and with dectectable conceit in his voice Cuthbert added, &quot;Also I was told that you had some information for me. I am curious, as to what such a young one has to offer me that I would find so important...&quot; <br>
